hat/sessionChat.ts:255:        id: 'composition-failed',\nfrontend/src/features/session/chat/sessionChat.ts:258:          snapshot.latest_composition_job.error_message ??\nfrontend/src/features/session/chat/sessionChat.ts:259:          snapshot.latest_composition_job.stop_reason ??\nfrontend/src/features/session/chat/sessionChat.ts:262:          snapshot.latest_composition_job.updated_at ?? snapshot.updated_at,\nbackend/app/models/story_outline.py:17:    bedtime_softening_note: str | None = None\nbackend/app/models/story_outline.py:32:    bedtime_goal: str | None = None\nbackend/app/models/story_outline.py:56:    bedtime_guardrail: str | None = None\nbackend/app/models/story_outline.py:62:            raise ValueError(\"story outline cards require at least one supporting beat\")\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:27:    COMPOSITION_CHUNK = \"composition.chunk\"\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:54:class CompositionChunkKind(str, Enum):\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:61:    COMPOSITION = \"composition\"\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:137:class CompositionChunkEventPayload(RealtimeContractModel):\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:142:    chunk_kind: CompositionChunkKind = CompositionChunkKind.DELTA\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:150:    def validate_chunk_body(self) -> CompositionChunkEventPayload:\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:151:        if self.chunk_kind == CompositionChunkKind.DELTA and not self.text:\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:154:        if self.chunk_kind == CompositionChunkKind.SEGMENT_SUMMARY and not self.summary:\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:244:class CompositionChunkRealtimeEvent(EphemeralSessionRealtimeEventBase):\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:245:    type: Literal[RealtimeEventType.COMPOSITION_CHUNK] = RealtimeEventType.COMPOSITION_CHUNK\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:246:    stage: Literal[WorkflowStage.COMPOSITION] = WorkflowStage.COMPOSITION\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:247:    payload: CompositionChunkEventPayload\nbackend/app/models/realtime.py:269:    | CompositionChunkRealtimeEvent\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:7:# - prompts/52-bedtime-safety-and-content-guidelines.md\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:11:    description: A bedtime-safe adventure with a clear destination, gentle bravery, and a warm return home.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:12:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep the journey wondrous rather than perilous; any danger should feel temporary, buffered by helpers, and resolved before sleep.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:16:      bedtime_payoff: The final image should land in shelter, reunion, or visible rest.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:21:        bedtime_notes: Avoid sharp reversals or loud triumph; let discoveries feel luminous and safe.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:38:        bedtime_notes: Keep the hero's courage rooted in reassurance from mentors, companions, or familiar rituals.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:55:        bedtime_notes: Let tension resolve early enough that the ending can linger in calm reflection.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:72:    description: A puzzle-forward bedtime story driven by clues, curiosity, and a reassuring explanation.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:73:    bedtime_safety_notes: Mystery should never feel menacing; clues can be strange, but the world must stay emotionally safe and readable.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:77:      bedtime_payoff: The reveal should repair uncertainty and make the world feel kinder than before.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:82:        bedtime_notes: Keep the unknown intriguing instead of eerie; every clue should feel like an invitation.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:99:        bedtime_notes: Let the investigation happen in familiar spaces with emotionally available companions.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:116:        bedtime_notes: Keep the payoff tender and emotionally soothing, not twisty or shocking.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:134:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep animal-scale stakes manageable and end with nesting, denning, or other visible signs of safety.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:138:      bedtime_payoff: The ending should emphasize home, family, and rhythmic natural quiet.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:143:        bedtime_notes: Keep humor kind and the mishaps tiny enough that they never feel upsetting.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:160:        bedtime_notes: Favor emotional reassurance, caregiving, and tactile coziness over plot intensity.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:177:        bedtime_notes: Water, wind, and night sounds should soothe rather than unsettle.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:195:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep interpersonal conflict mild, repair visible, and magic supportive instead of chaotic.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:199:      bedtime_payoff: End with closeness, belonging, and a felt sense of mutual care.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:204:        bedtime_notes: Make support explicit; the characters should feel emotionally available to one another.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:221:        bedtime_notes: Keep the silliness breezy and never mean-spirited; the laugh should settle into calm.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:238:        bedtime_notes: Let hurt feelings be named gently and healed clearly before the ending.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:256:    bedtime_safety_notes: Even when dream logic gets strange, maintain orientation through comforting guides, repeated motifs, and gentle landings.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:260:      bedtime_payoff: The ending should feel like a soft arrival into sleep itself.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:265:        bedtime_notes: Keep scene transitions smooth and reassuring so the surrealism never jars.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:282:        bedtime_notes: Pair every strange image with something grounding like blankets, snacks, or a trusted companion.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:295:          ending_style: surreal details fade into a cozy bedtime tableau\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:299:        bedtime_notes: Minimize plot complexity and favor patterned language, repetition, and soothing imagery.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:316:    description: Science-flavored bedtime stories driven by curiosity, observation, and awe rather than technical complexity.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:317:    bedtime_safety_notes: Keep scientific concepts accessible, reassuring, and emotionally warm; discovery should never become sterile or high-pressure.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:321:      bedtime_payoff: The world feels larger, kinder, and more connected by the end.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:326:        bedtime_notes: Let facts deepen awe and comfort rather than interrupt story flow.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:343:        bedtime_notes: Keep experiments small, reversible, and supported by encouraging adults or peers.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:356:          ending_style: success leads to quiet pride and bedtime wind-down\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:359:        description: Natural science and twilight exploration meet in a mellow, outdoorsy bedtime tone.\nbackend/app/data/genre_tone_catalog.yaml:360:        bedtime_notes: Keep the setting legible and friendly, with twilight framed as beautiful rather than ominous.\nbackend/app/models/intent_parser.py:80:                or action.extracted_values.job_kind != ChatToUIJobKind.COMPOSITION\nbackend/app/models/intent_parser.py:83:                    \"pause_writing must propose a composition pause_job action\",\nbackend/app/models/intent_parser.py:90:                or action.extracted_values.job_kind != ChatToU